Python 3.x

Required libraries:

opencv-python

numpy

playsound (or pygame as an alternative for sound playback)

threading (built-in)

Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/vnayhegde/motion-detection-opencv.git
cd motion-detection-opencv

Install the required Python packages:

pip install opencv-python numpy playsound pygame

Ensure you have a valid .wav sound file named motion_detected_sound.wav in the project directory for the audio alert.
